sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Hesap sahibi
    participant X as X sayfasi
    participant Ext as Extension
    participant Outbox as Local outbox
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant Worker as Worker

    User->>X: Sayfayi manuel acar
    Ext->>X: Yalniz gorunur DOM'u okur
    Ext->>Outbox: Payload + idempotency key
    Outbox->>API: POST /capture
    API->>DB: Inbox ve job transaction
    DB-->>API: Commit
    API-->>Outbox: 202 accepted
    Outbox->>Outbox: Teslim kaydini sil
    Worker->>DB: Pending job claim
    Worker->>DB: Feature/event/suggestion yaz
    DB-->>Worker: Commit ve audit
    Note over Outbox,API: Hata halinde exponential backoff; kayit silinmez
